                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 180/64.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Chile</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Third Assistant Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">S. S. Kaiser Wilhelm der Grosse</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Via wireless and Halifax</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-08-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 10, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Repeat to you, Gen. Carter, Capt. Hulse, Mr. Dawson, best thanks for your
                    attention and kindness.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Pedro Montt.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
